description:
Been dancing for 1-3 years?

Looking to become a more original BBoy?

Hitting a 'plateau'?

Find out the never-talked-about process for creating completely original moves that you can claim as your own with these advance creativity concepts!

Discover the strategies for:

  • Quickly creating original BBoy moves you can claim as your own
  • Step-by-step strategies for thinking 'outside of the box'
  • Becoming more of a 'beat-rider'

And much more!

Learn from BBoy Bminus from the Now Or Never crew the step-by-step strategy for breaking through your plateau and continuing in your improvement to become the original, recognized, unique bboy.
title: BBoy Blueprint - Advanced BBoy Creativity Concepts
